title: Jay Williams to Karlie Redd Interview
itunes:title: Jay Williams to Karlie Redd Interview
description:
Friday 8/3 - Today on the show we had former basketball player Jay Williams stop by and spoke on his new documentary ‘Best Shot’ & doing more in the community to impact our youth. Also, Charlamagne gives another Florida Man "Donkey of the Day" for attacking his ex girlfriends current boyfriend. Moreover, we had Karlie Redd stop by where she spoke about her newly engagement, being on Love and Hip Hop, and things got a little freaky near the end, and lets just say she got very anal about the topic.
